Ifeanyi Onuba, Abuja The out-going Permanent Secretary, Budget and National Planning, Mr Ernest Umakhihe, has handed the mantle of leadership to Mrs Olusola Idowu, urging her to effectively implement the mandate of the ministry. Umakhikhe, according to a statement from the ministry on Sunday, gave this charge to his successor during the handover ceremony at the ministry in Abuja. The out-going Permanent Secretary expressed gratitude to the management and members of staff of the ministry for their support during his short stay. Copyright PUNCH.
